snippet.title: Ground Divers - Exclusive Announcement Trailer (ft. Hironobu Kageyama) | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
The voice behind Dragon Ball Z's famous Cha-La-Head-Cha-La opening song, Hironobu Kageyama, sings the theme song to the upcoming Dig-Dug-Esque mining game, Ground Divers!
